# Philolexian Society backend web stuff

This is a repository of tools and configuration needed for regular
operation and maintenance of the [Philolexian
Society](http://www.philo.org/)'s web sites, such as:

* "Philowixian" (the main public-facing wiki)
* "Privowixian" (the private members-only wiki)

## Assumptions

7. Everything is under `$HOME/philo`.
7. `$HOME` is currently `/home/schmonz`.
